==Players== * [[Nate Davis (quarterback)|Nate Davis]]: Passing Yards-3000+ yards and 25 + touchdown passes * [[Dante Love]]: 70+ receptions, 1000+ receiving yards, and 7 touchdowns. * Darius Hill: 40+ receptions, 650+ receiving yards, and 7 touchdowns. * Frank Edmonds: 121 rushes, 466 rushing yards, 3.9yrds/per carry, and 6 touchdowns. * Chris Miller: All American First Team punter.
HB MiQuale Lewis only played 4 games following an ACL injury, but ran for 447 rushing yards, 4.9 yards/per carry, and 2 touchdowns. He also put up 111.8 rushing yards a game.
